text: Hey! It’s Matt Keeter! I was thinking this was similar to Antimony and lo and behold, this is a successor. I had studied your codebase for kokopelli and wrote a toy diffing algorithm in javascript based on your work there. How come kokopelli and antimony were abandoned, and you keep starting over on new projects? Did you discover a deadend with each of those?
